<section id="elements">
    <h1>Elements</h1>
    <p>All of Strapless's components happen to be HTML elements too. There are no classes to remember, just different ways to put together HTML tags. Here are some examples.</p>
</section>

<section id="main_element" class="info">
    <h1>&lt;main&gt;</h1>
    <p>The <em>main</em> element should give a high-level description of the page and a quick follow-up action.</p>
